details.message:
`004.001.003 Active_Asset`
- Test creates asset "Test Asset Gamma" with the following characteristics.
- Has asset type of "TAT-2. (Inheriting 8 data attributes and everything else...).
- Has PM Anchor date of 01/01/2024.
- Has asset status of "Collected".
- Linked to SMCT 001 chargeable account.
- Linked to "Testing Department". 
- Default crew of "Crewmate".
- Failure profile of "Whoops!" and failure type of "Spontaneous Combustion".
- Maintenance strategy of "The Thunderbolt Strategy".
- Asset standard of "LGTM".
- Part of system "CORE" which is a system type of "SYS-TYP"
- Has a maintenance manager "Chief Engineer Derrick".
